   Nantasenamat, Chanin, Mahidol Univ, Ctr Data Min \& Biomed Informat, Fac Med Technol, Salaya, Nakhon Pathom, Thailand.
   Hasan, Md Mehedi, Tulane Univ, New Orleans, LA 70118 USA.
   Manavalan, Balachandran, Korea Inst Adv Study, Seoul, South Korea.},
