   The, Jesse, Lakes Environm Res Inc, 170 Columbia St W Suite 1, Waterloo, ON N2L 3L3, Canada.
   Tan, Zhongchao, Tsinghua Univ, Dept Energy \& Power Engn, Beijing 100084, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.jclepro.2023.136959},
EarlyAccessDate = {APR 2023},
