   Zhang, Lifu, Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Remote Sensing \& Digital Earth, Beijing 100101, Peoples R China.
   Lin, Jiayuan, Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Mt Hazards \& Environm, Chengdu 610041, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.ufug.2015.03.003},
Keywords = {Aerial oblique imaging; Individual tree detection; Residential
