   Lallich, Stephane, Univ Lyon 2, Lab ERIC, F-69365 Lyon 07, France.
   Pham, Nguyen-Khang, Can Tho Univ, IRISA, Vietnam, Austria.},
Keywords = {High Dimensional Data; Random Forests; Oblique Decision Trees; Support
