   Rattanachoung, Nopporn, Kasetsart Univ, Fac Liberal Arts \& Sci, Dept Phys \& Mat Sci, Kamphaeng Saen Campus, Nakhon Pathom 73140, Thailand.
   Khojitmate, Sujira, Rajamangala Univ Technol Thanyaburi, Fac Engn, Dept Text Engn, Thanyaburi 12110, Pathum Thani, Thailand.},
