Affiliation = {Bengaly, C (Corresponding Author), Observ Nacl, BR-20921400 Rio De Janeiro, RJ, Brazil.
   Bengaly, Carlos; Alcaniz, Jailson, Observ Nacl, BR-20921400 Rio De Janeiro, RJ, Brazil.
