   Security and Identification},
Year = {2017},
Pages = {54-59},
Abstract = {With the development of machine learning and computer vision, we
   combined the image classification and malware detection in this work.
   Based on the technology of image classification, we achieved the
   detection of malware, using machine learning. In our work, we visualized
   the malware as a grayscale image and extracted texture features by Gabor
   filter. Depend on machine learning, we used extremely randomized trees
   as the classification and 10-fold cross validation to value it. Compared
