   Lyu, Yi; Yan, Hai-Xia; Guo, Rui; Hong, Jing; Wang, Yi-Qin; Xu, Jin, Shanghai Key Lab Hlth Identificat \& Assessment, Shanghai 201203, Peoples R China.
   Wu, Hai-Mei, Guangdong Prov Tradit Chinese Med Hosp, Guangzhou 510120, Peoples R China.
   Xiong, Yu-Jie, Shanghai Univ Engn Sci, Shanghai 201620, Peoples R China.
   Chen, Rui, Global Inst Software Technol, Suzhou 215163, Peoples R China.
   Huang, Wen-Yue, Shanghai Univ Tradit Chinese Med, Shuguang Hosp, Shanghai 201203, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1186/s12911-024-02666-1},
