   Tahir, Ahsen, Univ Engn \& Technol, Dept Elect Engn, GT Rd, Lahore 54890, Punjab, Pakistan.
   Khan, Muhammad Usman Ghani, UET, Al Khawarizmi Inst Comp Sci, Natl Ctr Artificial Intelligence, Lahore, Pakistan.},
