   Breaban, Ana-Ioana, Gheorghe Asachi Tech Univ Iasi, Fac Hydrotech Engn Geodesy \& Environm Engn, Dept Hydroameliorat \& Environm Protect, Prof Dimitrie Mangeron Blvd 67, Iasi 700050, Romania.
   Pfeifer, Norbert, Tech Univ Wien, Dept Geodesy \& Geoinformat, Karlspl 13, A-1040 Vienna, Austria.},
DOI = {10.3390/rs14020422},
Article-Number = {422},
Keywords = {UAS point cloud; segmentation; classification; machine learning; 3D
