   Spiers, Adam J., Max Planck Inst Intelligent Syst, Dept Hapt Intelligence, D-70569 Stuttgart, Germany.
   Morgan, Andrew S.; Dollar, Aaron M., Yale Univ, Dept Mech Engn \& Mat Sci, New Haven, CT 06520 USA.
   Srinivasan, Krishnan, Stanford Univ, Dept Comp Sci, Stanford, CA 94305 USA.
   Calli, Berk, Worcester Polytech Inst, Comp Sci Dept, Worcester, MA 01609 USA.},
DOI = {10.1109/TOH.2019.2958669},
Keywords = {Friction; Thumb; Robot sensing systems; Haptic interfaces; Actuators;
