   Li, Li; Garg, Aman, Huazhong Univ Sci \& Technol, Sch Mech Sci \& Engn, State Key Lab Intelligent Mfg Equipment \& Technol, Wuhan 430074, Peoples R China.
   Garg, Aman, NorthCap Univ, Dept Multidisciplinary Engn, Gurugram 122017, Haryana, India.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.molliq.2024.124498},
EarlyAccessDate = {MAR 2024},
