   Liu, Jiangang, Beijing Engn Res Ctr Cardiovasc Wisdom Diag \& Trea, Beijing, Peoples R China.
   Liu, Jiangang, Beihang Univ, Sch Engn Med, Beijing 100191, Peoples R China.
