Affiliation = {Wen, GR (Corresponding Author), Xi An Jiao Tong Univ, Sch Mech Engn, Xian 710049, Shaanxi, Peoples R China.
   Wen, GR (Corresponding Author), Key Lab Educ Minist Modern Design \& Rotor Bearing, Xian 710049, Shaanxi, Peoples R China.
