   Pagliaro, Antonio, Ist Nazl Fis Nucl, Sez Catania, Via Santa Sofia 64, I-95123 Catania, Italy.
   Pagliaro, Antonio, ICSC Ctr Nazl Ric HPC, Big Data \& Quantum Comp, I-40121 Bologna, Italy.},
DOI = {10.3390/electronics14091721},
