   Hoque, Ahasanul, Univ Kebangsaan Malaysia, Inst Perubahan Iklim, Pusat Sains Angkama ANGKASA, Ukm Bangi 43600, Selangor, Malaysia.
   Islam, Mohammad Tariqul; Kirawanich, Phumin, Mahidol Univ, Fac Engn, Dept Elect Engn, 25-25 Phuttamonthon 4 Rd, Nakhon Pathom 73170, Thailand.
   Soliman, Mohamed S., Taif Univ, Coll Engn, Dept Elect Engn, POB 11099, Taif 21944, Saudi Arabia.
