   Tonin, Fernanda Stumpf, Inst Politecn Lisboa, H \&TRC Hlth \& Technol Res Ctr, ESTeSL, Escola Super Tecnol Saude, Lisbon, Portugal.
   Pontarolo, Roberto, Univ Fed Parana, Dept Pharm, Curitiba, Brazil.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.chemolab.2024.105145},
