   Li, Yupeng, China Univ Geosci, Sch Automat, Wuhan 430074, Peoples R China.
   Siang, Lim C.; Li, Jin, Burnaby Refinery, Dept Proc Control Engn, Burnaby, BC V5C 1L7, Canada.},
